                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-428" type="given" value="JOEL HOLLOW"></interp>JOEL HOLLOW AY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 142.) I went to Mr. Clark's shop on the 7th of April, and found the prisoner there—I received this bad half-crown</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183805140051"></xptr>
               <p>from Mr. Clarke—I am sure it is the same—the prisoner was dis<lb></lb>charged on that occasion.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. FIELD</hi>. This half-crown and this shilling are both counterfeit.</p>
